dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Condor Peak quadrangle, Los Angeles County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. and Bruce Carter ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle CONDOR PEAK, CA 1995, NIMA 2352 I SW-Series V895"
"Prepared in cooperation with the Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History and the Angeles National Forest."
Includes 2 col. cross sections, quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
